{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/j0n7r5","slide":1,"text":"PetraVigil is built for the moment a shipping signal changes the decision clock. Instead of giving a team another alert or an opaque recommendation, it creates a visible path from the signal to a constrained procurement choice. Every data state is labeled, every scenario assumption is reviewable, and the final call remains with a human. This is evidence-first energy supply resilience: not autonomous buying, but faster, safer preparation for disruption."}
