{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/kbjo8u","slide":5,"text":"This architecture reflects what is actually present today. The analyst experience is a Next.js workbench over FastAPI, with strict Pydantic contracts. Behind it are the Gemini integration, signal mesh, NumPy scenario engine, OR-Tools optimizer, and a local SQLite repository for workflow and decision records. The supply network runs from a historical JSON projection, so the prototype can operate offline. PostgreSQL, Neo4j, and Redis are included in docker-compose as enterprise scaffolding, but we label them as not active runtime dependencies. That distinction is intentional and builds trust."}
