{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/tb4pyz","slide":6,"text":"This is the moment we would show live. We paste the demo shipping advisory and immediately see its provenance as user-entered. The app extracts and resolves the signal, displays the corridor risk, and stops for analyst confirmation. The judge can change closure severity, duration, alternative-route capacity, elasticity, run count, and seed. After confirmation, the system runs one thousand reproducible scenarios, compares four portfolios, and explains the selected option. Only then can a user record an approval—and that record is local only. This is a complete workflow, not a static dashboard."}
