{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/c0hiaf","slide":8,"text":"The business case starts with an operating decision, not a software feature list. Procurement leads need to choose a feasible posture early. Risk and trading teams need to understand distributional exposure. Refinery operators need alternatives that fit their crude diet. Public-sector planners need a shared, reviewable playbook. Today’s MVP delivers a scenario-led decision workflow with explicit provenance, uncertainty, and approval. The roadmap is deliberately clear: connect live AIS, news, prices, commercial availability, maps, and graph services. We are not claiming those live integrations exist today; we are showing the credible path to deployment."}
