{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/8nu50jyh","slide":10,"text":"The winning standard for AI decision tools\nis not autonomy. It is accountable speed.","textPreview":"The winning standard for AI decision tools | is not autonomy. It is accountable speed.","textChars":84,"textLines":2,"bbox":[72,120,950,130]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/to3m94f2","slide":10,"bbox":[72,342,220,0]}
