{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/7ml47exw","slide":10,"text":"It attacks the signal-to-decision bottleneck.","textPreview":"It attacks the signal-to-decision bottleneck.","textChars":45,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,402,238,55]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/sje5c3el","slide":10,"bbox":[356,342,220,0]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/dk76l8f6","slide":10,"text":"Meaningful AI","textPreview":"Meaningful AI","textChars":13,"textLines":1,"bbox":[356,365,238,26]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/1o7qpcb2","slide":10,"text":"LLM intelligence is bounded by deterministic controls.","textPreview":"LLM intelligence is bounded by deterministic controls.","textChars":54,"textLines":1,"bbox":[356,402,238,55]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/gnypw7ux","slide":10,"bbox":[640,342,220,0]}
