{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/dwrqxwba","slide":10,"text":"Make resilience a rehearsed decision—not a crisis improvisation.","textPreview":"Make resilience a rehearsed decision—not a crisis improvisation.","textChars":64,"textLines":1,"bbox":[102,557,958,30]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/cvi94rup","slide":10,"text":"PETRAVIGIL · EVIDENCE-FIRST ENERGY SUPPLY RESILIENCE","textPreview":"PETRAVIGIL · EVIDENCE-FIRST ENERGY SUPPLY RESILIENCE","textChars":52,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,654,500,16]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/9jw4kb","slide":10,"text":"PetraVigil deserves to win because it treats the hard part of AI decision-making seriously. It understands that a disruption is not just a prediction problem; it is a signal-to-decision bottleneck. It uses AI where AI helps—structuring uncertain input and explaining results—and uses deterministic engineering where feasibility matters. It is typed, tested, reproducible, and constrained. And it is viable because it respects human authority and states its limits. The outcome we are building toward is simple: make resilience a rehearsed decision, not a crisis improvisation."}